    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Telluri Genetrici res publica <expan><abbr>Cuicul<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>tanor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> templum fecit <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Lepidus Tertullus <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> dedicavit <lb n="3"/>simulacrum deae acrolithum <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> Iulius Honoratus <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>amen</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>er</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>etuus</ex></expan> dono dedit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: C. Iulius Lepidus Honoratus war im Jahr 194 n. Chr. kaiserlicher Legat in Numidien.</p>
            </div>
